From: DockLite SSL & Testing Improvements
Subject: [PATCH] Add ACME SSL management with lego and comprehensive test infrastructure

This patch adds:
1. ACME SSL management using lego library (replaces certbot dependency)
2. DNS-01 and HTTP-01 challenge support
3. Comprehensive Go test infrastructure with testhelpers
4. TypeScript test setup with Vitest
5. SSL v2 API endpoints

---
